title: Is This the First Caravan Member to Be Granted Asylum in the United States?
subtitle: A cynical attempt to smear asylum seekers in the 2018 “caravan” of immigrants is actually a 2009 photo from a pornographic website.
author: Alex Kasprak
vclaim: A meme purporting to include an image of a Honduran asylum seeker and “caravan” member named Susana González shows the first woman to be granted asylum in the United States in that group.
